+# Metadata
+
+> Since v1.20
+
+GoReleaser creates some metadata files in the `dist` folder before it finishes
+running.
+
+These are the options available:
+
+```yaml
+# .goreleaser.yaml
+#
+metadata:
+  # Set the modified timestamp on the metadata files.
+  #
+  # Templates: allowed.
+  mod_timestamp: "{{ .CommitTimestamp }}"
+```
